<p class="ayah 14-7" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَأَذَّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">proclaimed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَئِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"If</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَكَرْتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you are thankful,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَأَزِيدَنَّكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely I will increase you;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَئِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرْتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you are ungrateful</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">My punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَشَدِيدٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) surely severe."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/14:7" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1757"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>7<span class="icon ri