<p class="ayah 14-13" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieved</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِرُسُلِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to their Messengers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَنُخْرِجَنَّكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Surely we will drive you out</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَرْضِنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">our land</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَتَعُودُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely you should return</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِلَّتِنَا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">our religion."</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَوْحَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So inspir