<p class="ayah 14-16" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن وَرَآئِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Ahead of him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَهَنَّمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Hell,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُسْقَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and he will be made to drink</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّآءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">water</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَدِيدٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">purulent.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/14:16" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1766"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>16<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
