<p class="ayah 14-18" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّثَلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(The) example</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieve</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِرَبِّهِمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in their Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْمَـٰلُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَرَمَادٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) like ashes</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱشْتَدَّتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">blows furiously</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرِّيحُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the wind</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَاصِفٍ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">stormy.</span></span><span class="