<p class="ayah 14-20" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِعَزِيزٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">great.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/14:20" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1770"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>20<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 14-21" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبَرَزُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they will come forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَمِيعًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">all together,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then will say</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلضُّعَفَـٰٓؤُاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the weak</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتَكْبَرُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">were arrogant,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Indeed we,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَبَعًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">followers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَهَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so can</span></