<p class="ayah 14-22" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And will say</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشَّيْطَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Shaitaan,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُضِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has been decided</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَمْرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the matter,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَدَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">promised you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعْدَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a promise</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَقِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) truth.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَوَعَدتُّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And I promised you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَخْلَفْتُكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but I betrayed you.