"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the wrongdoers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلِيمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">painful."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/14:22" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1772"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>22<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 14-23" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأُدْخِلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And will be admitted,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and did</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَنَّـٰتٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) Gardens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجْرِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">flows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْتِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">underneath it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the rivers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِدِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) abide forever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it</span