<p class="ayah 14-24" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Do not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَيْفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">how</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ضَرَبَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah sets forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَثَلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the example,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَلِمَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a word</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَيِّبَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَشَجَرَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) like a tree</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَيِّبَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصْلُهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its root</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثَابِتٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) firm</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَفَرْعُهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and its branches</span></span><span class="word staticWo