<p class="ayah 14-30" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجَعَلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they set up</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَندَادًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">equals</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّيُضِلُّواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that they mislead</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلِهِۦ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">His Path.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَمَتَّعُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Enjoy,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَصِيرَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your destination</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّارِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Fire."</span></span></span> <a href