<p class="ayah 14-51" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِيَجْزِىَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So that Allah may recompense</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">each</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">soul</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(for) what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَسَبَتْ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it earned.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَرِيعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Swift</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحِسَابِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) the reckoning.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/14:51" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="1801"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>51<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 14-52" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">This</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلَـٰغٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a Message</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلنَّاسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the mankind,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِيُنذَرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that they may be warned</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِيَعْلَمُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that they may know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَـٰهٌ وَٲحِدٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) One God,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِيَذَّكَّرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and that may take heed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">men</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَلْبَـٰبِ</span><span class="en second ltr